Commands

Set up

git version
git config --list
git config user.name
git config user.email 
cat /home/anno/.gitconfig
git config --global color.ui true 

Basic stuff 

git clone URL
git log 
git init // Two ways to get a git repository. 
git add . // Adds whole directory. 
git status 
git commit 
git show // Shows the last commit. 
git apply 
git commit -a // Everything that has been tracked and modified and staged for commit. 
git add NAME // stages files for commit. 

